        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">happydrain</P><P>he is the evil brother to happyhugs and very opposite ...</P><P>he relishes in death and decay and sings of peoples demise .. he ses the beauty in death and as the worms eat at your entrails and maggots suck upon your eyes then and only then can you find happiness<BR>.. YAY ?? </P><P>the small gnome has been spotted speaking to a paladin dwarf in butcherblock mountains.. lets listen in and see what we can hear...</P><P></P><P>The small gnome scowls at the paladin that is making the trek in the same direction. they head for the boat in the butcher block mountains..</P><P>the regal dwarf clutches the hilt of his sword as he notices the gnome eyeing him up. and begins to speak," Small one I have no toil with you I keep me blade sheathed lets just keep our distance from one another on this journey."</P><P>The small gnome muttereds incoherently with madenss a few times .. bearded things bah ... it hasnt got a beak..</P><P>Then the small gnome looked up at the dwarf as if enlightened and spoke directly to him unwaivering and hie eyes pierced at the very soul of the dwarf probing and began to say </P><P>"Methinks when you die.. Me shall make you my slave and make you fight again for my cause. Your feelings and emotions matter not. I will control your body for that is my art. It shall dance and move to my every whim. It shall do my bidding ithout error. I will however allow you sentient thought. So you can loathe and abhor your actions. So you can feel the pan and misery you cause. Yet your body will still go on under my command. It shall in the end do the bidding of its dark master. Your rules and laws wont allow you to strike me down in this life will it .. Honor .. "</P><P>The gnome begins to cackle insanely and looks off in the distance..</P><P>Then once more his sanity seems to come back and again fixates his gaze on the dwarf and preceeds.</P><P>" where was I yes.. honor that thing you hold so dear and clutch to .. You protect the weak you smite evil. My pet you dont know that you are just a flowerin my garden. Gardens grow in seasons. And eventually some of the flowers wither and die. But a good farmer picks a strong one and brings it back in another form making it stronger... it just gets rid of the bad parts about it. makes it a good strain of flower. You my precious are a flower to me. You are a warrior of the light now but in death will make you a warrior of darkness. For that is my ways. So i have spoken so shall it be done. "</P><P>The gnome begins looking past the dwarf at the docks in the distance ...</P><P>The dwarf unsheaths his blade and spouts in a regal tone, " I challenge you gnome for you are foul and evil bring forth your weapon and meet me this day in battle".</P><P>The gnome shakes his head a bit confused the madness returning to his eyes..</P><P>The gnome in a differnt tone begins to speak. <BR>"Im just a poor helpless farmer what quarrel do I have with you " I just tend the fields where am I ?? I just need to get to freeport to meet me wife to get the new seeds for the next season." </P><P>The dwarf astonished look in his eyes looks about the area for the source of the evil that might be infiltrating the gnome.</P><P>the dwarf speaks. "Good farmer i shall protect you from this evil that is attacking you.. I shall escort you to the ship to freeport and see you safe in your journey"</P><P><BR>The dwarf pats the gnome on the back and says ," Ill take the lead to protect our path "</P><P>the dwarf begins to make way to the docks. As the dwarf turns his back on the gnome the innocent face of the gnome turns into a deep wry vile smile. And from beneath the tatered cloak of the gnome a dagger apears with an evil glow about it. the gnome places it up his sleeve for easier acess.</P><P>The dwarf checks his footing on the docks and a slight hint of fear washes over him. The gnome can sense feel it .</P><P>The gnome begins to speak in the inocent voice."what is wrong sir dwarf ? "</P><P>the gruff dwarf speaks ,"Ah dwarves are made for battle not for boats i never learned to swim so i dont like these docks ."</P><P>The gnome looking helpful says," Well good sir dwarf you were kind enoug to protect me to here. I shall return the favor and help you in your journeys."</P><P>the dwarf begins to loosen his armor.</P><P><BR>The gnome begins to speak,"</P><P>"Good dwarf keep your armor on what if the evil is about us surely you will need to be prepared for battle what better place to strike then here ?"</P><P>the dwarf pondersand utters," You are right gnome I shall keep my wepons and armor on me this journey"</P><P>The gnome offers his hand and helps steady the dwarf as they make way to the end of the dock together.</P><P>The gnome looks down at the water and says," When i look down in the water i can see my future I can see whats to come. What do you see ?"</P><P>The dwarf hesitantly looks a little at the edge dock and not wanting to loose face steps and begins to peer over the side but his constricting armor wont allow him the proper angle.</P><P>the gnome with helping hands says," ahh let me steady you so you can peer my good friend "</P><P>the gnome helps the dwarf peer into the water to see his reflection.</P><P><BR>"So what is it that thou see my good friend ? "smiled the gnome</P><P><BR>the dwarf beins to speak," i see the ripples of the waves that are ...</P><P>The dwarves voice trials off as the gnome thrusts the blade deep into the dwarves back and pushes the dwarf over the side of thedock. the dwarf turns to late and the weight of his armor pulls him under the water .. the last sight he saw was the gnome cacking madly on the docks and the words of the gnome embedded in his mind over and over </P><P><BR>You are a warrior of the light now but in death will make you a warrior of darkness. For that is my ways. So i have spoken so shall it be done..</P><P>The water begins to enter his lunges as the light above became dimmer and dimmer .. trying to undo his armor but he knows it is to late.. and his last thoughts were of the gnomes face and what he said</P><P><BR>You are a warrior of the light now but in death will make you a warrior of darkness. For that is my ways. So i have spoken so shall it be done..</P><P><BR>the cackling gnome sits on the dock and begins to mutter insanely to his doll that he brings forth from a pocket..</P><P>ahh me precious it is time for i have a warrior to do me bidding yes yes ..</P><P>The gnome begins weaving his hands in intricate patterns and the water before him begins to ripple and bubbles begin to come forth. The ripples slowly go to the shore line, and the undead warrior slowly walks from the ocean..</P><P>the gnome smiles at his new creation and cackles</P><P></P><P><img src="http://www.wam.umd.edu/~brandysj/cook.jpg"></P><P><BR>happydrain 0th level necro on rz</font></td>
